But when I found out

00:18:12.270 --> 00:18:13.660
Le was my son,

00:18:14.830 --> 00:18:15.620
I felt like

00:18:16.510 --> 00:18:17.220
I wasn't alone anymore.

00:18:18.920 --> 00:18:19.980
I didn't feel so lonely.

00:18:20.110 --> 00:18:21.290
I felt my life had

00:18:22.030 --> 00:18:23.010
a continuation.

