Gao Hui and Feng Rui

00:20:05.260 --> 00:20:06.740
must be treating him very well.

00:20:07.460 --> 00:20:08.100
I believe he's enjoyed

00:20:11.140 --> 00:20:12.740
plenty of family warmth.

00:20:18.980 --> 00:20:19.460
Siting,

00:20:21.540 --> 00:20:22.700
don't be too sad.

00:20:23.340 --> 00:20:24.740
What matters is that he is doing well.

00:20:25.700 --> 00:20:26.940
And have you thought

00:20:27.740 --> 00:20:28.740
over these years,

00:20:29.260 --> 00:20:30.420
it's been the best choice

00:20:31.340 --> 00:20:32.580
for the child to stay with Rui?

00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:38.300
♪Who hasn't wondered if their life
would stay blank and bare?♪

