I want to see him every day

00:21:11.300 --> 00:21:12.220
at his school gate,

00:21:13.580 --> 00:21:15.940
to see which classmates
he's playing with

00:21:16.820 --> 00:21:19.980
and who his teachers are

00:21:20.780 --> 00:21:22.820
and to see if he is having a good time
every day.

00:21:23.820 --> 00:21:25.060
I don't know what I should do

00:21:25.060 --> 00:21:27.180
to make up for these years.

00:21:27.820 --> 00:21:29.100
About the absence in his life,

00:21:30.780 --> 00:21:31.860
what should I do?

00:21:31.900 --> 00:21:33.820
♪If we look back,
a lingering warmth stays♪

00:21:33.940 --> 00:21:35.020
♪In the dialogue
where time and space part ways♪

00:21:35.060 --> 00:21:35.460
I think

00:21:35.980 --> 00:21:37.220
you're doing a great job now.

00:21:37.620 --> 00:21:37.900
Come on,

00:21:39.700 --> 00:21:40.020
let's drink.

